This module adopts the same governance shape as terraform-aws-vpc:
unified Foundation Plan §15.2 tagging, the central reusable CI workflow
in devotica-labs/terraform-shared-config, and conftest policies from
devotica-labs/terraform-policies.

Defaults for the account-level password policy are aligned with
the CIS AWS Foundations Benchmark v3.0 (§1.5–1.11) and the RBI Cyber
Security Framework for Scheduled Commercial Banks (§III.2).

